==English==

===Etymology===
Alteration (due to {{m|en|breadth}}) of {{der|en|enm|handbrede}}, {{m|enm|hondbrede|t=handbreadth}}; equivalent to {{com|en|hand|breadth}}. Cognate with {{cog|stq|Houndebratte|t=handbreadth}}, {{cog|fy|hânbreedte|t=handbreadth}}, {{cog|nl|handbreedte|t=handbreadth}}, {{cog|de|Handbreite|t=handbreadth}}, {{cog|sv|handsbredd|t=handbreadth}}, {{cog|no|håndsbredd|t=handbreadth}}, {{cog|is|handbreidd|t=handbreadth}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

